Classes in com.poesys.db.dao.update used by com.poesys.db.dao
IUpdate
          An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a data transfer object (DTO) in the database.
IUpdateBatch
          An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a batch of data transfer objects (DTOs) in the database.
IUpdateCollection
          An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a collection of data transfer objects (DTOs) in the database.
IUpdateSql
          An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IUpdate, IUpdateBatch, or IUpdateCollection object to build a SQL UPDATE statement for a data transfer object (DTO).
IUpdateWithParameters
          An interface for a Command-pattern class that updates a database based on a set of parameters contained in a data transfer object (DTO).

           An implementation of the IUpdateBatch interface that contains the base code for updating a batch of objects in the database.
UpdateByKey
          An implementation of the IUpdate interface that updates a data transfer object (DTO) using a SQL statement defined in an IUpdateSql object, identifying the object in the database using the primary key of the DTO.
UpdateCollectionByKey
           An implementation of the IUpdateCollection interface that contains the base code for updating a collection of objects in the database.
